          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1620662654944-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1620662654944-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Separate the <strong>egg yolk[s]</strong> from the <strong>whites</strong> by cracking your <strong>egg[s] </strong>over a small bowl and catching the<strong> yolk </strong>in the shell</p><p>Transfer the yolk from one shell half to the other several times, until all the whites are in the bowl and you are left with the yolk in the shell</p><p>Tip: Hold on to those egg whites! They’re perfect for meringues or a protein-rich omelette (they freeze well too!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1620662689023-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1620662689023-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1620662689023-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1620662689023-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
