          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1620662689023-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add most of your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save some for garnish!) and the <strong>egg yolk[s] </strong>to a small bowl</p><p>Season with a few generous grinds of <strong>black pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a little splash of <strong>cold water </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>carbonara sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1620662700144-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1620662700144-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
