          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1620662700144-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stock is absorbed, add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 1 min further then take the risotto off the heat</p><p>Add the <strong>carbonara sauce</strong> and give everything a really good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy carbonara risotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Mix the sauce through the risotto quickly to avoid scrambling the egg!</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1620662713520-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
